createenderlink.ponder.ender_vault_shari: Sharing Items via the Ender Vault
The Ender Vault can share its contents like an Ender Chest
The Ender Vault has a slot for setting its frequency
Placing an item in the slot determines the frequency
Ender Vaults with the same frequency share their contents
When wearing Engineers' Goggles, the player can see how many Ender Vaults are currently linked
createenderlink.ponder.ender_vault_contr: Ender Vaults can be integrated into contraptions
Vaults in a contraption also share contents with other vaults on the same frequency
createenderlink.ponder.ender_tank_sharin: Sharing Fluids via the Ender Tank
The Ender Tank can share its fluid contents
The Ender Tank has a slot for setting its frequency
Placing an item in the slot sets the frequency
Ender Tanks with the same frequency share their contents
When wearing Engineers' Goggles, the player can see how many Ender Tanks are currently linked
